<promed@promedmail.org>
[Some serious criticisms have been omitted from the article. In the
meantime, the disease continues to spread; on Fri, 18 Nov 2005, the Chinese
Ministry of Agriculture reported new outbreaks in Xiaoyi City of Shanxi
Province and Urumqi City of the Xinjiang Uygur Autonomous Region. We wish
the Chinese authorities the best of luck and success in the huge endeavour
they have undertaken. - Mod.AS]
